        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nThis change is needed to fix a bug introduced recently in the cds-ui helm charts.  2 values being passed as env settings are interpreted as non-strings (one as a Boolean, the other as an int) and helm deploy on sdnc is failing because the value is missing quotes.  I tested this fix in my WindRiver env and verified that it fixes the problem",
